{"tid":870509,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【岳華逝世】《珠光寶氣》飾夫妻 蔡少芬聞岳華死訊激動痛哭","createTime":"2018-10-21T07:41:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-21T08:54:25.000Z","uid":78546,"like":2,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"07de618e793505948383240333bc678be980f420","tid":870509,"uid":78546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-21T07:41:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20181021&amp;s=7018882&amp;a=58818804\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20181021%26s%3D7018882%26a%3D58818804&d=BqY1nZ9xAMQx3w6LkQeDmKS6uTmBE%2FuUnOR61Sj848o%3D&h=b00f0f77\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20181021%26s%3D7018882%26a%3D58818804&h=f0fc5c14\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20181021&amp;s=7018882&amp;a=58818804</a> <br />\n<br />\n近日無綫深夜重播2007年開拍的劇集《珠光寶氣》，劇中蔡少芬（Ada）與岳華發展忘年戀，之後兩人更結為夫婦，兩人頗多對手戲。<br />\n<br />\n今日Ada接受傳媒訪問時，一度激動痛哭，她大讚岳華是一個好好先生，而且極有風度。《蘋果》今日致電Ada，她說：「我真係唔想講，一諗起我又忍唔住喊。」<br />\n<br />\n至於在無綫另一劇集《巾幗梟雄》、飾演岳華四姨太的鄧萃雯，收到拍檔病逝消息後極度愕然，她接受本報電話訪問時稱：「咁橋你打畀我，我正正拍緊類似嘅劇情（ViuTV新劇），真係人生如戲。」<br />\n<br />\n雯女續說：「我知道佢有病，我有擔心。生命好無常，聽到呢個消息真係好難過，我好耐冇見佢，唔知佢情況點。每個人面對生命都唔一樣，我陪阿娟（羅慧娟）行過呢段路，有啲人面對疾病，會更加懂得珍惜、更加積極面對人生，唔當自己係一個病人。」"},{"pid":"5b192a675a77be5e0aac20383361f92200826f36","tid":870509,"uid":144784,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-21T07:43:05.000Z","msg":"琴晚睇珠光寶氣先見到佢 有邊個諗到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62fbcc597706cfac90d27da5cec7b930bd827c51","tid":870509,"uid":78546,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-21T07:44:37.000Z","msg":"對Ada太差 搞成咁"},{"pid":"6d63c5dae2a010f850e2aab14fbdeb9c11b7ec77","tid":870509,"uid":44391,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-21T07:47:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"69f435465d86512f407d0bd447625d294dfb4391","tid":870509,"uid":92859,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-21T08:12:35.000Z","msg":"岳華：痛恨搞亂香港的人，支持反佔中<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/870200\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/870200</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"33eedb02204a68a97d6d8863cf0b498d36778949","tid":870509,"uid":208940,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-21T08:36:45.000Z","msg":"Rip"},{"pid":"52dfe3837b53cc8719b4fa0c535318b48b7e2edb","tid":870509,"uid":550,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"62fbcc597706cfac90d27da5cec7b930bd827c51","tid":870509,"uid":78546,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-21T07:44:37.000Z","msg":"對Ada太差 搞成咁"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-21T08:51:01.000Z","msg":"對adap仲好"},{"pid":"3425bdcdd9ca7ac33948a1bd2936e6cca08aaa31","tid":870509,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"62fbcc597706cfac90d27da5cec7b930bd827c51","tid":870509,"uid":78546,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-21T07:44:37.000Z","msg":"對Ada太差 搞成咁"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-21T08:54:25.000Z","msg":"笑左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}